These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-1::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, siglo, vegafina, blend
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, trike, boat, helicopter
1. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the car##1
2. the havana-smoker is the person driving the helicopter##1
3. the person driving the boat is on the right of the person driving the car##1
4. the siglo-smoker is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the blend-smoker is on the left of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Cigar          | blend | vegafina | siglo | havana   |
| Transport   | trike  | car     | boat   | helicopter |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: lavender, green, lilac, pink
The people use 4 different means of transport: trike, taxi, van, train
1. the person who likes pink is the person driving the taxi##1
2. the person who likes lavender is on the far right##1
3. the person who likes green is on the right of the person who likes pink##1
4. the person who likes pink is on the right of the person driving the van##1
5. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person driving the trike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |
| Color   | lilac | pink | green | lavender    |
| Transport   | van    | taxi      | trike | train |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: begonia, balloon-flower, aconite, poppy
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, june, november, october
1. the person who's birthday is in november is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
2. the person who growsbegonia is the person who's birthday is in september##1
3. the person who's birthday is in june is on the far right##1
4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who growspoppy##1
5. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |      3      |       4       |
| Flower         | begonia | poppy | aconite   | balloon-flower |
| Birthday   | september   | november | october | june         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, hot-chocolate, lemonade, mirinda
There are 4 different favourite colors: orange, ivory, aquamarine, azure
1. the person who likes ivory is the person drinking mirinda##1
2. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
4. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
5. the person who likes orange is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | mirinda | hot-chocolate | fanta  | lemonade      |
| Color         | ivory | azure   | aquamarine | orange |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-5::.
4 different games are played: go, bridge, mah-jongg, scrabble
House: ranch-style, colonial, townhouse, tower
1. the person playing bridge is on the left of the person playing go##1
2. the townhouse house is on the right of the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the person playing scrabble is on the left of the tower house##1
4. the colonial house is on the right of the townhouse house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |  2   |    3     |      4      |
| Game   | scrabble | mah-jongg | bridge | go |
| House    | ranch-style       | tower | townhouse | colonial     |

