.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-6::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: ambient, blues, gospel, indie
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, pall-mall, ritmeester, dunhill
1. the fan of blues is on the far right##1
2. the fan of indie is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
3. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the pall-mall-smoker##1
4. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
5. the dunhill-smoker is on the right of the ritmeester-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | indie | gospel | ambient | blues |
| Cigar           | oliveros      | ritmeester | dunhill | pall-mall    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-7::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, sports, martial-arts, documentary
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, coffee, 7up, mirinda
1. the person drinking 7up is on the far left##1
2. the person watching documentary movies is on the far right##1
3. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
5. the person watching sports movies is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2      |     3     |   4    |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts | sports | crime | documentary  |
| Beverage           | 7up | cola | mirinda       | coffee |

