.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-8::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, bolivar, alhambra, ritmeester
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, sports, family, drama
1. the person watching drama movies is on the right of the bolivar-smoker##1
2. the person watching drama movies is the ritmeester-smoker##1
3. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the pall-mall-smoker##1
4. the alhambra-smoker is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
5. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |    3     |    4     |
| Cigar         | alhambra | pall-mall      | bolivar | ritmeester |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie          | sports | family     | drama    |

