.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-11::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, golf, snowboarding, basketball
The people have 4 different jobs:  doctor, journalist, dancer, lawyer
1. the dancer is on the right of the doctor##1
2. the lawyer is on the right of the dancer##1
3. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person who's sport is rowing##1
4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is golf is the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2   |       3       |   4   |
| Sport      | snowboarding | golf  | rowing | basketball |
| Job   | doctor  | dancer | lawyer           | journalist   |

