.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-12::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, july, november, may
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, water, tea, cola
1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
3. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person drinking 7up##1
4. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |  3   |   4    |
| Birthday   | july | december | may | november  |
| Beverage           | cola | water      | tea | 7up |

