.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-13::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: salsa, soul, rock, classical
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, musical, thriller, scientific
1. the person watching scientific movies is the fan of salsa##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
3. the fan of rock is the person watching thriller movies##1
4. the fan of rock is on the left of the person watching musical movies##1
5. the fan of classical is on the right of the fan of salsa##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |   2    |   3    |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | rock | soul  | salsa | classical   |
| Movie-Genre        | thriller | musical | scientific    | fantasy |

