2. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the far left##1
3. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1
4. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
5. the person who's hobby is puzzles is on the left of the person eating pepper##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4        |
| Hobby           | collecting | skydiving    | puzzles    | baking |
| Food   | banana      | artichoke | watermelon | pepper       |

