.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-1-20::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: apricot, ivory, aquamarine, black
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, sprite, tea, lemonade
1. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1
2. the person drinking sprite is on the left of the person who likes black##1
3. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person who likes aquamarine##1
4. the person who likes black is the person drinking lemonade##1
5. the person drinking cola is on the left of the person who likes ivory##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3     |     4      |
| Color   | apricot | aquamarine | ivory | black   |
| Beverage     | tea  | cola    | sprite       | lemonade |

 